					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="value-icon">üîß</div>
					<h3>Professional Service</h3>
					<p>
						Our team of experienced technicians is trained to handle all your HVAC needs with
						professionalism, expertise, and attention to detail.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="value-icon">‚úì</div>
					<h3>Quality Workmanship</h3>
					<p>
						We take pride in our work and stand behind every installation, repair, and maintenance
						service we provide. Your satisfaction is our priority.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="value-card">
					<div class="value-icon">üíº</div>
					<h3>Customer Commitment</h3>
					<p>
						We're committed to providing honest assessments, fair pricing, and reliable service.
						No surprises, just quality HVAC solutions.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="service-area">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Serving Bastrop County & Central Texas</h2>
			<p class="section-subtitle">
				Based in Rosanky, TX, we proudly serve residential and commercial customers throughout
				Bastrop County and the surrounding areas. From historic downtown Bastrop along Main Street to rural properties near Lake Bastrop, we're your local HVAC experts.
			</p>
			<div class="area-features">
				<div class="area-item">
					<h3>Local Expertise</h3>
					<p>We understand Central Texas weather‚Äîthe scorching summers that push past 100¬∞F and the occasional winter freeze. Our solutions are designed for the unique demands of Bastrop County's climate.</p>
