					<li>Professional and courteous service on every job</li>
					<li>Honest assessments and transparent pricing</li>
					<li>Quality workmanship backed by our commitment to excellence</li>
					<li>Respect for your home and property</li>
					<li>Clear communication throughout the service process</li>
					<li>Expert advice to help you make informed decisions</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Experience the Difference</h2>
			<p>Discover why customers trust String Prairie Heating & Air for their HVAC needs</p>
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<a href="https://book.housecallpro.com/book/String-Prairie-Heating--Air/df82ded280ce43f4a9ee6ee6d36aef76?v2=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-light">üîñ Book Online</a>
